  <h3>BreadcrumbPage</h3>
  <p>Represents the current page in the breadcrumb (last element).</p>

  <h3>BreadcrumbSeparator</h3>
  <p>Visual separator between breadcrumb items.</p>

  <h3>BreadcrumbEllipsis</h3>
  <p>Indicates truncated items, used when there are many levels.</p>

