  <h2 id="accessibility">Accessibility</h2>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Semantic navigation:</strong> Uses <code class="inline-code">&lt;nav aria-label="Breadcrumb"&gt;</code></li>
    <li><strong>Ordered list:</strong> <code class="inline-code">&lt;ol&gt;</code> for hierarchy</li>
    <li><strong>Current page:</strong> <code class="inline-code">aria-current="page"</code> on BreadcrumbPage</li>
    <li><strong>Separators:</strong> <code class="inline-code">role="presentation"</code> and <code class="inline-code">aria-hidden="true"</code></li>
    <li><strong>Keyboard:</strong> Standard Tab navigation</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Best practices</h2>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Consistency:</strong> Use the same variant as your design system</li>
    <li><strong>Clear hierarchy:</strong> Show only relevant levels</li>
    <li><strong>Smart truncation:</strong> Use BreadcrumbEllipsis for long paths</li>
    <li><strong>Mobile:</strong> The breadcrumb automatically adapts with flex-wrap</li>
    <li><strong>Performance:</strong> Components are static (no JavaScript)</li>
  </ul>

